title: Match nas Estrelas
overview: Match nas Estrelas is an astrological dating show. There are twelve episodes in which a single person, who represents one of the zodiac signs, is introduced to four bachelors or bachelorettes with whom they have different astral compatibilities. Chatting and chemistry: everything can be a sign of what the stars want. After the dates, it's time to make a decision: listen to or ignore the stars?
